    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Hi team. \nWe are facing the same issue using vue-instantsearch `4.21.0`.\n\nWe have a big list of facets, I was thinking to create a configuration array like bellow and then loop with dynamic component pattern in Vue, but looks like can't loop inside the `ais-dynamic-widgets`.\n\nconfig would be something like this: \n```js\nconst facetsConfig = [\n// ...\n{\n    name: 'AisRefinementList',\n    label: 'Brand',\n    description: '',\n    enabled: true,\n    componentProps: {\n      attribute: 'brand_name',\n      searchable: true,\n      searchablePlaceholder: 'Search brands...',\n      limit: 10,\n      showMore: true,\n      showMoreLimit: 20,\n    },\n  },\n// ...\n]\n```\n\nand then we could loop over the config: \n```html\n<AisDynamicWidgets>\n  <template\n    v-for=\"facet in facetsConfig\"\n    :key=\"facet.name\"\n  >\n    <AisPanel v-if=\"facet.enabled\">\n      <template #header=\"{ hasRefinements }\">\n        <p>{{ facet.label }} <span v-if=\"!hasRefinements\">(no results)</span></p>\n      </template>\n      <component\n        :is=\"facet.name\"\n        v-bind=\"facet.componentProps\"\n      />\n    </AisPanel>\n  </template>\n</AisDynamicWidgets>\n```",
